{"title":"“功臣号”坦克  为纪念“八一”建军节二十三周年而作","authors":["蓝曼"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":8,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为纪念“八一”建军节二十三周年而作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓝曼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年十月一日，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开国大典的那天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在天安门前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和着军乐的节奏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走过一队队的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"步兵，骑兵和炮兵。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接着是装甲部队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一阵摩托声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"第一辆大坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出现在阅兵场上。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炮塔的顶上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"飞舞着一面红旗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“八·一五”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日本帝国主义者投降的时候，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们把铁路炸了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把工厂烧了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把武器丢在河里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把坦克炸坏了轮子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧坏了机器，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把零件扔在山沟里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶着寒风和雪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们走进森林；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冒着地雷的危险，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们钻进山洞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在哈福我们找到了轮子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在黑河我们找到了发电机，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"以公主岭我们找到了电邦浦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喷油嘴是在满洲里找到的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过千辛万苦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们把一件件零件找齐。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有电瓶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"机器不能发动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人力代替动力马达，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从这条街，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉到那条路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"排气筒开始冒烟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这已经死去了的坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"终于复活在革命者的手里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦克做了我们的老师，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们开始了学习。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在风雪吹打的夜里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们和它整夜作伴。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"冬天我们为它取暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"落雨给它披上雨衣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身体脏了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家抢着给它洗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在炎热的暑天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们钻进车里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象进了蒸笼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着满身大汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们躺在车下修理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滚得满身油泥。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用手擦一把汗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脸涂得象锅底。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就这样的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教会了我们驾驶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教会了我们修理，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"教会了我们射击。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三下江南，（注）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦克和我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"始终在一起。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起踏过北满的大雪原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起渡过结冰的松花江。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在漆黑的夜里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一起顶着雪风前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们攻下了靠山屯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歼灭了敌人的骑兵旅，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在德惠外围"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摧毁了敌人“永久性”的工事。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把敌人的蜘蛛脚切断，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把敌人困在瓮里。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在进关的路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"履带扬起万里风沙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坦克手们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举着指挥的小红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驰过了平原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过了山地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一月十四日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋勇地打进了天津。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在坦克炮的吼叫里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人的地堡开了花。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人举起了白旗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"参加了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中华人民共和国开国典礼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它走在装甲部队的最前面，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧接着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无数辆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"威武地驶过"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席的面前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象一个忠勇的战士"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受着伟大领袖的检阅。……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这钢铁的战士，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“功臣号”坦克，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正驻守在祖国的边疆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捍卫着祖国的土地。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（注）“江南”指松花江南。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}